{"tid":1125918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔中案凸顯一國兩制無保障　國台辦：台灣不應對香港事務說三道四","createTime":"2019-04-26T04:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T04:58:03.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"73d684f47df270dad37f7ee3f309f8c6b37f2f02","tid":1125918,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190425/1430763.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190425%2F1430763.htm&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreNUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=c9926a8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190425/1430763.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港佔中案於24日宣判，三名佔領運動發起人判刑16個月，其中朱耀明緩刑兩年，陳健民、戴耀廷即時入獄，陸委會並在第一時間指出，判決結果印證一國兩制未能尊重民眾政治權。對此，國台辦發言人馬曉光今（25日）砲轟民進黨當局罔顧香港法治，對香港事務說三道四，是其慣於混淆是非、顛倒黑白的又一表現。<br />\n<br />\n國台辦下午透過書面聲明回應佔中案判決，馬曉光表示，當年持續79天的非法佔中，嚴重衝擊香港特區法治，對香港的繁榮穩定、香港民眾的正常生活秩序都帶來嚴重損害。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，「中央政府堅定支持香港特區依法懲治非法佔中的主要組織者和策劃者」，民進黨當局罔顧香港法治，對香港事務說三道四，是其慣於混淆是非、顛倒黑白的又一表現。<br />\n<br />\n佔中案在24日宣判，陸委會除了在第一時間發表聲明，發言人邱垂正在25日的例行記者會更重申占中行動肇因北京毫無誠信，沒有兌現對香港普選的承諾，是香港民眾爭取民主普選的和平抗爭行動。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，政府對參與者遭到刑事判決表達遺憾，此事也突顯中共主導的一國兩制毫無保障可言，「一方面強調講好一國兩制故事，一方面卻壓縮香港民主自治與自由人權空間，可說自曝其短。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 佔中案凸顯一國兩制無保障 國台辦：顛倒黑白 | ETtoday大陸 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190425/1430763.htm#ixzz5mAoRBGi9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190425%2F1430763.htm%23ixzz5mAoRBGi9&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreNUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=37327852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190425/1430763.htm#ixzz5mAoRBGi9</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"0b9af76b4ce8792017502a0e6b15b64491174627","tid":1125918,"uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:47:48.000Z","msg":"國台辦親自示範一國兩制下<br />\n你連響自己地方出聲嘅權利都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c93b23b4083671fa43f7d0acbe39b3f88c2870","tid":1125918,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"大家都係咁中國人喎"},{"pid":"d116bd42ca218b3855b7b0a098f37577c2c12daf","tid":1125918,"uid":61589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:50:39.000Z","msg":"碌撚：香港人不應對台灣事務說三道四<br />\n<br />\nD口吻似撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47fd7283cea197dca52a010b8dac73c3757e2be","tid":1125918,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"今日香港 明日台灣"},{"pid":"3631d921c53e2ccff371a6b70839831998aa571b","tid":1125918,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"如果大家都係中國人點解唔可以評？<br />\n支那咁講咪即係台灣唔係中國人"},{"pid":"0a7749c18ebc1c69dcb91fff338a2bfc57719162","tid":1125918,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"又話台灣係支国一部份?<br />\n<br />\n但又唔可以干涉別國內政?"},{"pid":"35a6943766daf1228828366293648b983fc2757b","tid":1125918,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3631d921c53e2ccff371a6b70839831998aa571b","tid":1125918,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"如果大家都係中國人點解唔可以評？<br />\n支那咁講咪即係台灣唔係中國人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"鄰國可以評論㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13879843035823107242876596a4dd2af16f6cd2","tid":1125918,"uid":133695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nqb8GHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqb8GHi.